

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>SwapHub | How It Works</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-..." crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --red: #e63946;
      --orange: #f77f00;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --black: #1a1a1a;
      --gray: #cccccc;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background-color: var(--white);
      color: var(--black);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--red), var(--orange));
      color: var(--white);
      position: relative;
    }

    .logo {
      max-width: 50px;
      position: absolute;
      top: 1rem;
      left: 1rem;
    }

    .subtitle {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .steps {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2rem;
      padding: 2rem;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .step {
      background-color: var(--white);
      border: 2px solid var(--gray);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 1rem;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    .step:hover {
      transform: scale(1.02);
      border-color: var(--black);
    }

    .step i {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: var(--orange);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }

    .step-content h2 {
      color: var(--orange);
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .step-content p {
      color: #333;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>How It Works</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Your go-to campus platform to Buy, Sell, Donate, and Rent</p>
  </header>

  <section class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h2>1. Sign Up / Log In</h2>
        <p>Create your account to access all SwapHub features tailored for students.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <i class="fas fa-user-tag"></i>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h2>2. Choose Your Role</h2>
        <p>Be a Seller, Buyer, Donor, or Renter — or switch roles anytime.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <i class="fas fa-box-open"></i>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h2>3. List or Browse Items</h2>
        <p>Add your products or browse existing listings by others.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h2>4. Connect & Transact</h2>
        <p>Chat securely and complete the swap on or off-campus.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2025 SwapHub. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>